  "slug": "chocolate-overnight-oats",
  "title": "Chocolate Overnight Oats",
  "subtitle": "Make it before bed, eat it before work.",
  "excerpt": "Chocolate Overnight Oats. A home-cook's recipe from Rebecca's collection, kept in the family rotation.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook, a recipe she's made many times in her own kitchen.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Chocolate Overnight Oats. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Made the night before; ready when you wake up. Adjust the liquid to suit your usual breakfast bowl.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What you need",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
